appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We are working on an upgrade! Keep an eye out for a big upgrade of the app in the near future! No action required from you, just keep the app updated.
Some new features are:
New name: Deltares Aquality app
Fresh new look and feel
Manual input for measurements
and more!

title: Nitrate App

creator: Deltares
descriptionHtml:
Aquality is a reliable tool that aims to improve water quality by measuring, tracking and analysing nutrient levels in water and soil.

A simple and easy to use app for farmers, researchers and others who actively participate in research on the impact of agricultural practices on water quality. By taking measurements you can make better informed decisions, detect hot spots of nitrate losses and optimise agricultural practices.

What’s New:
- new name, Deltares Aquality instead of Nitrate app
- new refreshed look and feel
- update and delete your measurements
- add measurement results manually
- filter measurements by day, week, month and year
- order measurement equipment in the app webshop

What can you do with the app?
- measure and register nitrate values in water and soil
- measure and register salinity values in water
- easily take measurements with the in-app camera scan
- add measurement results manually
- view your historical measurement data
- view different measurements on a map
- filter your measurements by days, weeks, months and years
- compare your measurements with the map view
- order your measurement equipment in the app webshop

About Deltares:
Deltares developed the Aquality app to empower farmers and advisors working together to improve water quality. The results generated with the app are indicative results to support better decision making around improving water quality for all.
descriptionShort: A tool for measuring, tracking and analysing nutrient levels in water and soil.
